<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,654,1585]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308">
The first description of the larva of this species was realized by 
<bibRefCitation author="Navas, L." box="[862,1013,654,679]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" pagination="373 - 398" refId="ref16811" refString="Navas, L. (1915) Neuropteros nuevos o poco conocidos (IV serie). Memorias de la Real Academia de Ciencias y Artes de Barcelona, 11 (3), 373 - 398." type="journal article" year="1915">Navás (1915)</bibRefCitation>
as the previous accounts were simply brief reports about the discovery of the eggs and 1 
<superScript attach="left" box="[714,724,689,703]" fontSize="6" pageId="21" pageNumber="308">st</superScript>
instar larvae (
<bibRefCitation author="Ragonot, E. L." box="[884,1047,693,718]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" pagination="47" refId="ref17353" refString="Ragonot, E. L. (1878) [Ascalaphus longicornis] Seance du 27 Aout 1878. Bulletin de la Societe Entomologique de France, (5) 8 [= 47], cxx." type="journal article" year="1878">Ragonot 1878</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="McLachlan, R." box="[1059,1251,693,718]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" refId="ref16691" refString="McLachlan, R. (1878) Ascalaphus longicornis, eggs and larvae, exhibited October 2 1878 Exhibition &amp; c .. Proceedings of the Royal Entomological Society of London, 26, l." type="book" year="1878">McLachlan 1878</bibRefCitation>
) while other old descriptions were inconclusive (
<bibRefCitation author="Lacroix, J. L." box="[518,675,729,754]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" pagination="65 - 100" refId="ref16539" refString="Lacroix, J. L. (1923) Faune des Planipennes de France. Ascalaphidae. Bulletin de la Societe d'Etude des Sciences Naturelles d'Elbeuf, 41, 65 - 100." type="journal article" year="1923">Lacroix 1923</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Rabaud, E." box="[690,845,729,754]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" pagination="433 - 499" refId="ref17322" refString="Rabaud, E. (1927) Etude biologique des larves de quelques Planipennes. Bulletin Biologique de la France et de la Belgique, 61, 433 - 499." type="journal article" year="1927">Rabaud 1927</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Rousset, A." box="[867,1039,729,754]" pageId="21" pageNumber="308" pagination="164 - 178" refId="ref17391" refString="Rousset, A. (1973) Morphologie externe et caracteres distinctifs des larves de trois especes d'Ascalaphes [Nevropteres, Planipennes]. Bulletin de la Societe Entomologique de France, 78, 164 - 178." type="journal article" year="1973">Rousset (1973)</bibRefCitation>
redescribed the larvae, comparing them with congeners.
</paragraph>
